00:00:01.270 --> 00:00:04.000
VALERA ZAKHAROV: Hello, welcome
to our Green At Google

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:06.310
and Authors At Google
Talk Series.

00:00:06.310 --> 00:00:08.010
My name is Valera Zakharov.

00:00:08.010 --> 00:00:11.800
And today, we have a pretty
uncomfortably exciting talk

00:00:11.800 --> 00:00:13.440
for you today.

00:00:13.440 --> 00:00:16.370
We have with us, a local
San Francisco-based

00:00:16.370 --> 00:00:19.150
author, Ozzie Zehner.

00:00:19.150 --> 00:00:21.090
And the book is called
"Green Illusions--

00:00:21.090 --> 00:00:23.720
The Dirty Secrets of Clean
Energy and the Future of

00:00:23.720 --> 00:00:27.170
Environmentalism." And the book
has been causing shock

00:00:27.170 --> 00:00:30.810
waves, as "The Sunday Times"
reported recently.

00:00:30.810 --> 00:00:32.600
And it's been pretty eye
opening actually, and

00:00:32.600 --> 00:00:35.290
interesting to follow some of
the debates raging out there

00:00:35.290 --> 00:00:37.570
on various internet resources.

00:00:37.570 --> 00:00:42.570
Meanwhile, Ozzie has been
