alternatives as fossil fuel

00:38:33.430 --> 00:38:37.500
extenders, not replacements.

00:38:37.500 --> 00:38:39.140
So thank you very much.

00:38:39.140 --> 00:38:41.490
I look forward to giving your
book to other people to help

00:38:41.490 --> 00:38:44.210
them, educate them.

00:38:44.210 --> 00:38:47.980
But I would like to
