enabling

00:54:25.800 --> 00:54:27.700
technology or research--

00:54:27.700 --> 00:54:29.720
a Department of Efficiency
instead of a

00:54:29.720 --> 00:54:31.880
Department of Energy.

00:54:31.880 --> 00:54:36.670
And also things like removing
zoning restrictions that

00:54:36.670 --> 00:54:39.820
prevent density in certain
urban contexts can end up

00:54:39.820 --> 00:54:41.770
having a big impact.

00:54:41.770 --> 00:54:45.845
And so that's probably the
direction I would do.

