in the Mojave Desert to

00:59:30.480 --> 00:59:31.930
power the entire world.

00:59:31.930 --> 00:59:34.820
There's enough wind power to
power 100 times what we need

00:59:34.820 --> 00:59:36.050
and these kinds of things.

00:59:36.050 --> 00:59:37.710
And really, these are
just a failure

00:59:37.710 --> 00:59:38.420
in the way of thinking.

00:59:38.420 --> 00:59:41.050
I mean of course if you ask a
ridiculous question, you can

00:59:41.050 --> 00:59:42.850
find a ridiculous answer.

00:59:42.850 --> 00:59:47.460
And I mean the Mojave
Desert may be the

00:59:47.460 --> 00:59:49.540
Saudi Arabia of solar.

00:59:49.540 --> 00:59:53.730
But if we were to cover it with
solar cells, and cover

00:59:53.730 --> 00:59:57.310
the world's deserts with solar
cells, it would destroy

00:59:57.310 --> 01:00:00.440
