within a single generation,

01:00:00.440 --> 01:00:03.520
just because of the toxins, the
fossil fuels that would be

01:00:03.520 --> 01:00:07.950
required, the other climate
gases that are produced, that

01:00:07.950 --> 01:00:09.610
are many times worse than CO2.

01:00:09.610 --> 01:00:12.160
If you take that little dot of
solar energy that we get

01:00:12.160 --> 01:00:14.790
currently, or wind power that
we get currently, and then

01:00:14.790 --> 01:00:19.820
multiply those side effects by
something like 10,000, that's

01:00:19.820 --> 01:00:21.070
what you're looking at.

01:00:21.070 --> 01:00:23.460
So you just get another set of
side effects with alternative

01:00:23.460 --> 01:00:24.470
energy technologies.

01:00:24.470 --> 01:00:28.510
And they all rely
on fossil fuels.

01:00:28.510 --> 01:00:30.360
Thermal solar has the
same side effects.

01:00:30.360 --> 01:00:33.580
When you get back down to it,
you end up with the same types

01:00:33.580 --> 01:00:34.190
of side effects.

01:00:34.190 --> 01:00:37.870
The high cost of thermal solar
reflects the fossil fuels that

01:00:37.870 --> 01:00:38.960
are behind the stage.

